tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 35, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-11 10:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860722035,45974302,2202]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=37784933]e471167749[/uid] (2026-03-11 10:37):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，光伏电源长线是赌一个行业见底反弹么。[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>电池不是  电网是跟算电  光伏是战争延续的欧洲需求重提  你们连逻辑都不懂？", "lou": 1167, "content_length": 71, "reply_to": 860722035, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773197219}, {"pid": 860723767, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 54, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-11 10:49", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860723381,45974302,2204]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42680170]你看看你？[/uid] (2026-03-11 10:46):[/b]<br/><br/>可能主要是看车头赚钱了吧，原油这波肯定是吃饱了，然后设备这边如果是元旦后第一天追的，就已经杀到成本线了，图形确实烂的吓人。自己亏，别人赚，心态就不好了。[/quote]<br/>我120撤的原油 提前一天撤的石油股票<br/>整个论坛有我这种明牌的有几个？", "lou": 1168, "content_length": 68, "reply_to": 860723381, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773197351}, {"pid": 860724603, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-11 10:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860724146,45974302,2206]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42051801]skwh[/uid] (2026-03-11 10:51):[/b]<br/><br/>卧槽，光伏这个逻辑有点意思[/quote]<br/>你看欧洲天然气不就懂了  所以我的视角和你们不一样的", "lou": 1169, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 860724146, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1773197678}, {"pid": 860724931, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 25, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-11 10:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=860724660,45974302,2206]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67045282]颜控正义日记[/uid] (2026-03-11 10:54):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，电池是由于比亚迪新技术发布，导致大家对新技术路径有预期导致涨的吗[/quote]<br/>今年开始首批量产<br/>MD 你们真不看消息的？", "lou": 1170, "content_length": 41, "reply_to": 860724660, "from_client": "